source.name: Foreclosure Heatmap
source.description: The City of Oakland’s Foreclosed and Defaulted Residential Properties Registration, Inspection and Maintenance Program requires owners or the beneficiary and/or trustee pursuing property foreclosure and/or their agents to register, inspect, and potentially maintain their residential properties to protect the health and safety, livability, appearance and social fabric of our neighborhoods.
